Reviews

FAQ

Frequently Asked Questions

Where can I see the verified real account results?

We have our live real account track record on Myfxbook. Join Telegram Channel for updates.

What currency pairs should I use?

Recommended: AUDCAD, AUDNZD & NZDCAD
Additional pairs (Works but not recommended): EURUSD, GBPUSD, USDJPY, USDCHF, USDCAD, AUDUSD

Which platform does it work?

Currently, it works on MT4(Metatrader 4). In the future MT5 will be updated.

Do you provide set files?

Yes

What risks settings available?

We have Low, mid, significant & high. Along with this you can set Fixed lot, Dynamic lot based on Equity/Balance.

Do I get future updates for free?

Yes

Does it pass funding challenges?

Yes, Our EA was not built for funding programs thought, but many clients have used it and succeeded. 

Do you have feature to set daily drawdown limit?

Yes. you can set the percentage value. Helps for funding program.

What broker do you recommend to use?

All brokers support our EA. But we recommend TickMill, EXNESS & RoboForex

What VPS do you recommend?

we are using FXVM & Amazon VPS, so far the best VPS we have used.

What payment methods do you accept?

We Accept PayPal, Credit/debit card & Crypto Currencies.

Do you have official Telegram Channel?

Yes, @algofxmoney
